This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper mentions the creation of a new dataset with annotations of landmarks, which suggests that it may also belong to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. The use of a self-supervised model and adversarial learning also suggests that the paper may belong to the multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
